613
00:48:06,209 --> 00:48:08,413
I don't know
what's goin' on... I...

614
00:48:11,872 --> 00:48:13,661
I don't know
what happened to Big Dave.

615
00:48:13,761 --> 00:48:15,517
I know some of it.

616
00:48:15,585 --> 00:48:18,716
Irregullarities in the books, they said.
Can I explain it?

617
00:48:19,808 --> 00:48:21,848
You don't have to
