618
00:48:21,953 --> 00:48:24,735
I did help him cook the books, Ed.
I did do that.

619
00:48:31,297 --> 00:48:32,409
Should I...

620
00:48:34,145 --> 00:48:37,658
Should I tell you
why I changed the books?

621
00:48:40,801 --> 00:48:43,386
You don't have to
tell me anything.

622
00:48:44,737 --> 00:48:46,493
No, no, no!

623
00:48:47,777 --> 00:48:49,118
Jesus Christ!

624
00:49:03,457 --> 00:49:05,115
