625
00:49:05,184 --> 00:49:08,599
Anyone could open 'em up
and make sense of the whole goddamn store.

626
00:49:13,057 --> 00:49:14,944
I knew we'd pay for it.

627
00:49:15,040 --> 00:49:16,535
I don't care what it costs!

628
00:49:16,641 --> 00:49:19,870
This is when you come together.

629
00:49:19,969 --> 00:49:21,430
Well, that's awfully
