630
00:49:21,697 --> 00:49:24,599
The hell with it.
The hell with it, Eddie.

631
00:49:24,705 --> 00:49:26,527
This is when you come together.

632
00:49:26,625 --> 00:49:28,479
This is family.

633
00:49:31,777 --> 00:49:34,875
They're just people
like you and me, Ed.

634
00:49:35,137 --> 00:49:36,566
Remember that.

635
00:49:38,113 --> 00:49:39,968
Just people.

636
00:49:40,065 --> 00:49:44,255
They gotta put up the big front
so that people will trust 'em with their money.

637
00:49:44,352 --> 00:49:46,687
This is why the big lobby, Ed.

638
00:49:46,785 --> 00:49:51,422
But they put their pants on
one leg at a time just like you and me.

639
00:49:53,088 --> 00:49:56,536
They, too, use the toilet, Ed,
in spite of appearances.

640
00:49:56,641 --> 00:49:59,575
And their money will be secured
by the barber shop.

641
00:49:59,681 --> 00:50:02,550
A rock.
A rock, the barber shop.

642
00:50:02,657 --> 00:50:04,380
Mr. Raffo.

