you keep your mouth shut.

684
00:52:40,992 --> 00:52:43,643
I get the lay of the land,
I tell you what to say.

685
00:52:43,745 --> 00:52:46,876
No talking out of school.
What's out of school?
Everything's out of school.

686
00:52:46,944 --> 00:52:49,399
I do the talking.
You keep your trap shut.

687
00:52:49,505 --> 00:52:51,479
I'm an attorney. You're a barber.
You don't know anything.

688
00:52:54,464 --> 00:52:55,358
Okay.

689
00:52:55,424 --> 00:52:57,791
Good. Any questions,
give me a ring.

690
00:52:57,889 --> 00:53:00,125
Turandot suite.
If I'm out, leave a message.

691
00:53:01,281 --> 00:53:04,096
Sure you don't want anything?
No? Okay.

692
00:53:04,192 --> 00:53:06,080
You're okay, pal.

693
00:53:06,337 --> 00:53:08,573
You're okay, she's okay,
