and the flapjacks, honey.

695
00:53:17,536 --> 00:53:18,911
There they were,

696
00:53:21,760 --> 00:53:23,899
All going about their business.

697
00:53:25,985 --> 00:53:27,872
It seem like I knew a secret,

698
00:53:27,936 --> 00:53:31,285
A bigger one, even,
than what had really happened to Big Dave,

699
00:53:31,393 --> 00:53:34,142
Something none of them knew.

700
00:53:34,240 --> 00:53:36,629
Like I had made it to the outside somehow,

701
00:53:36,736 --> 00:53:39,257
And they were all still struggling
way down below.

702
00:54:01,792 --> 00:54:02,937
Ann.

703
00:54:04,160 --> 00:54:05,469
Hello, Ed.

704
00:54:06,305 --> 00:54:08,443
