707
00:54:23,841 --> 00:54:27,899
Course you know that Doris
had nothing to do with it.

708
00:54:28,000 --> 00:54:30,040
Nothing at all.

709
00:54:30,496 --> 00:54:32,285
I know.

710
00:54:33,089 --> 00:54:35,227
