715
00:54:58,976 --> 00:55:00,023
Yeah.

716
00:55:00,128 --> 00:55:04,056
We went camping last summer
in Eugene, Oregon.

717
00:55:04,160 --> 00:55:07,607
Outside Eugene, Ed.

718
00:55:09,536 --> 00:55:10,518
Yeah?

719
00:55:10,624 --> 00:55:14,235
