There's a great deal of fear.

730
00:55:46,335 --> 00:55:50,110
You know how certain circles
would-would find it,

731
00:55:50,208 --> 00:55:51,190
The knowledge, a threat.

732
00:55:51,296 --> 00:55:53,597
They-they try to limit it, and...

733
00:55:53,696 --> 00:55:57,438
Ann, would you like to come in,

734
00:55:57,536 --> 00:56:00,122
Sit down?

735
00:56:00,224 --> 00:56:02,134
Maybe have a drink.

736
00:56:06,848 --> 00:56:09,466
Sometimes knowledge
is a curse, Ed.

737
00:56:11,295 --> 00:56:13,881
After this happened,

738
00:56:13,984 --> 00:56:15,260
Things changed.

739
00:56:17,663 --> 00:56:18,743
Big Dave...

740
00:56:22,784 --> 00:56:25,151
He never touched me again.

741
00:56:27,968 --> 00:56:29,495
Tell Doris not to worry.

742
00:56:29,568 --> 00:56:32,088
I know it wasn't her.

743
00:56:33,088 --> 00:56:34,778
Perhaps this will
bring it out

744
00:56:34,880 --> 00:56:36,374
Finally.

745
00:56:36,608 --> 00:56:40,121
Perhaps now
it will all come out.

746
00:57:08,512 --> 00:57:09,973
It stinks.

747
00:57:10,240 --> 00:57:11,800
But it's true.

748
00:57:11,904 --> 00:57:14,140
I don't care it's true, it's not true.
It stinks.

749
00:57:14,207 --> 00:57:16,695
